high_descs: walk through the hallway and go to the diningtable.
pick up the knife from the table.
walk through the hallway until you get to a lettuce that is on the floor.
Cut the lettuce from the box and then close the box.
turn around and go to the sink.
Put the knife on the top of the sink.
Turn around and walk out of the bathroom and go open the lettuce box that is on the floor.
take a piece of lettuce of box.
take it to the bathroom and stand in front of the sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink, wash it, then remove it.
Leave the bathroom and go to the sidetable.
Put the lettuce down next to the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: get a piece of lettuce and take it to the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the end of the hall, then turn left into the kitchen, go to the diningtable.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn right at the doorway, then turn left before you get to the dresser by the hall, go to the lettuce in the hall.
Slice the lettuce in the cardboard box.
Turn right, go to the bathroom sink.
Place the knife on the counter beside the left handle of the sink.
Turn around to the lettuce.
Grab a slice of lettuce out of the box.
Turn right and head back to the bathroom sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it up.
Head back to the sidetable, and go across to the microwave.
Place the lettuce on the sidetable with the microwave in the front left corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean slice of Lettuce on the SideTable beside a plate.

high_descs: Go straight and turn right down the hall, taking a left at the end to the room with a diningtable just ahead.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Return to the hall and go down the hall the way you came, taking a left at the first short path, to the lettuce on the floor.
Slice the head of lettuce in the box.
Turn right and enter the sink.
Place the knife on the rim of the sink.
Return to the box you sliced the lettuce at.
Pick up the lettuce.
Return to the sink in the bathroom to the right.
Wash the lettuce with water in the sink and pick the lettuce back up.
Go back to the sidetable where you got the knife and go to the end towards the microwave.
Place the lettuce down on the sidetable to the left of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed and cut piece of Lettuce on a SideTable.
